{
  "info": {
    "name": "HITProduct API",
    "_postman_id": "hit-product-api-v1",
    "description": "Bo test Auth va User. Register/Login tu luu accessToken; refreshToken nam trong cookie HttpOnly. Forgot Password gui OTP; dien bien otp truoc khi Reset Password. Google Login tra redirect de mo trong trinh duyet.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000/api/v1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "accessToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "otp",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Cac endpoint xac thuc nguoi dung: dang ky, dang nhap, lam moi token, dang xuat. refreshToken duoc quan ly qua httpOnly cookie.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"displayName\": \"Nguyen Van A\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Dang ky tai khoan moi. Dang ky xong la dang nhap luon (issue tokens + tao session).\n\n**Validation:**\n- `email`: bat buoc, phai la email hop le\n- `password`: bat buoc, toi thieu 6 ky tu\n- `displayName`: bat buoc, khong duoc de trong\n\n**Response 201:**\n```json\n{\n  \"statusCode\": 201,\n  \"message\": \"Dang ky thanh cong.\",\n  \"data\": { \"accessToken\": \"<jwt>\" }\n}\n```\nHeader tra ve co `Set-Cookie: refreshToken=...; HttpOnly; Path=/api/v1/auth`.\n\n**Errors:**\n- `400`: Validation that bai\n- `409`: Email da ton tai"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status 201\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "  console.log('accessToken da duoc luu.');",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Body chi co accessToken (khong lo refreshToken)\", () => {",
                  "  pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('accessToken');",
                  "  pm.expect(json.data).to.not.have.property('refreshToken');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Co cookie refreshToken (HttpOnly)\", () => {",
                  "  pm.expect(pm.cookies.has('refreshToken')).to.be.true;",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Dang nhap. Body tra ve accessToken, refreshToken nam trong httpOnly cookie.\n\nScript tu dong luu `accessToken` vao bien collection.\n\n**Response 200:**\n```json\n{\n  \"statusCode\": 200,\n  \"message\": \"Dang nhap thanh cong.\",\n  \"data\": { \"accessToken\": \"<jwt>\" }\n}\n```\n\n**Errors:**\n- `400`: Validation that bai\n- `401`: Email hoac mat khau khong dung"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "  console.log('accessToken da duoc luu.');",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Co accessToken, khong co refreshToken trong body\", () => {",
                  "  pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('accessToken');",
                  "  pm.expect(json.data).to.not.have.property('refreshToken');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Co cookie refreshToken (HttpOnly)\", () => {",
                  "  pm.expect(pm.cookies.has('refreshToken')).to.be.true;",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh-token",
            "description": "Lay accessToken moi khi accessToken het han. KHONG can body: server doc refreshToken tu cookie (Postman tu gui cookie).\n\nAp dung token rotation: refreshToken cu bi vo hieu, cookie duoc cap moi qua Set-Cookie.\n\n**Response 200:**\n```json\n{\n  \"statusCode\": 200,\n  \"message\": \"Cap token moi thanh cong.\",\n  \"data\": { \"accessToken\": \"<jwt_moi>\" }\n}\n```\n\n**Errors:**\n- `401`: Thieu cookie / token khong hop le / het han / session khong ton tai"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "  console.log('accessToken moi da duoc cap nhat.');",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Co accessToken moi\", () => {",
                  "  pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('accessToken');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/logout",
            "description": "Dang xuat khoi thiet bi hien tai. KHONG can body: server doc refreshToken tu cookie, xoa session tuong ung va clear cookie.\n\n**Response 200:**\n```json\n{\n  \"statusCode\": 200,\n  \"message\": \"Dang xuat thanh cong.\"\n}\n```"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', '');",
                  "  console.log('accessToken da duoc xoa khoi bien.');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout All Devices",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/logout-all",
            "description": "Dang xuat khoi TAT CA thiet bi (xoa toan bo session cua nguoi dung) va clear cookie.\n\n**Yeu cau xac thuc:** `Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}`\n\n**Response 200:**\n```json\n{\n  \"statusCode\": 200,\n  \"message\": \"Dang xuat tat ca thiet bi thanh cong.\"\n}\n```\n\n**Errors:**\n- `401`: Thieu hoac accessToken khong hop le / het han"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', '');",
                  "  console.log('Tat ca tokens da duoc xoa.');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Change Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"oldPassword\": \"password123\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"matkhaumoi123\",\n  \"logoutOtherDevices\": true\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/change-password",
            "description": "??i m?t kh?u v? t?y ch?n ??ng xu?t c?c thi?t b? kh?c. Session hi?n t?i ???c gi? l?i. Y?u c?u access token c? sessionId."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test(\"C? c? loggedOutOtherDevices\", () => {",
                  "  pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property(\"loggedOutOtherDevices\");",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Forgot Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/forgot-password",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Gui OTP dat lai mat khau. Response khong lam lo email co ton tai."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Reset Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/reset-password",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"otp\": \"{{otp}}\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"newPassword123\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Dat lai mat khau bang OTP. Dien bien collection {{otp}} tu email."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Google Login - Start OAuth",
          "protocolProfileBehavior": {
            "followRedirects": false
          },
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/google",
            "description": "Khong tu theo redirect. Mo header Location trong trinh duyet; callback tra JSON accessToken va dat refreshToken cookie."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Redirect 302 sang Google\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(302));",
                  "pm.test(\"Co Google Location\", () => {",
                  "  pm.expect(pm.response.headers.get(\"Location\")).to.include(\"accounts.google.com\");",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Users",
      "description": "API ho so; can Bearer {{accessToken}}.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get My Profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/users/me",
            "description": "Lay ho so nguoi dung hien tai; khong tra passwordHash."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test(\"Khong lo passwordHash\", () => {",
                  "  pm.expect(pm.response.json().data).to.not.have.property(\"passwordHash\");",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Update My Profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/users/me",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"displayName\": \"Updated User\",\n  \"avatarUrl\": \"https://example.com/avatar.png\",\n  \"defaultQuizSize\": 20\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Cap nhat displayName, avatarUrl va defaultQuizSize."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test(\"Profile duoc cap nhat\", () => {",
                  "  const data = pm.response.json().data;",
                  "  pm.expect(data.displayName).to.eql(\"Updated User\");",
                  "  pm.expect(data.defaultQuizSize).to.eql(20);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "_Health Check",
      "description": "Kiem tra server dang chay.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Ping Server",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "http://localhost:3000/",
            "description": "Kiem tra server co dang chay khong. Khong co prefix /api/v1."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Server dang chay\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
